y":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:15:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌, 不如問下點解而家的士無八達通啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20120802/photo/0802-00176-013b1.jpg?t=1506496090634\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20120802%2Fphoto%2F0802-00176-013b1.jpg%3Ft%3D1506496090634&h=2a7034cb&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n你覺得有呢部野, 班仆街仲可以濫收車資咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地尻吹果啲附加費用現金收囉<br />\n而且有隧道費都唔會跟標收錢啦<br />\n咪又係自己入條數，屌"},{"pid":"fb7cbe0ce16fbd98abdc5c6cd9d438755fc8adc8","tid":415650,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:32:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"623a415e61af22135ee90c040ff2a29377ea4095","tid":415650,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:32:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3eb186ea059891096e13e985ea6158b865039ef6","tid":415650,"uid":108351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T12:00:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌, 不如問下點解而家的士無八達通啦</blockquote><br />\n用八達通點收你齊頭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5f9e576a2bec3bb5e14a107a71e9c4e8a96e76","tid":415650,"uid":40257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T12:06:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實大陸堅係有好多野過左香港<br />\n港豬肯接受呢個事實未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原因更本就係自己都有責任<br />\n政府唔推創科自己招至今日乜都俾人過曬怪邊個<br />\n香港人又唔肯試新野 hktv，viutv 就係一個好例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾曬機會我地，結果冇人珍惜同支持<br />\n人地淘寶乜野大特價就放下呢啲成見變左大家都係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到尾，人地成功帶到電子貨幣入黎<br />\n港豬們咪又係狗衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n預左俾人話五毛<br />\n至少我一次淘寶都未用過對得住自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n假鈔超越全球添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n監控又係超越全球添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n芝麻信用我諗全世界過多500年都唔會有另一個國家會用<br />\n<br />\n五毛我就唔知你係咪<br />\n但諗嘢唔全面你就一定係（或者有心講嘢唔全面）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n稻草人謬誤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望你唔好偷換概念<br />\n假鈔監控我冇話好<br />\n除去大陸呢個因素，呢樣電子貨幣concept 帶得起的話的確會改善好多野<br />\n<br />\n我只係想帶出<br />\n大陸近年的確係呢啲創科野方面有爆炸力<br />\n呢啲係我地要反思嘅地方<br />\n共享概念, uber, gobeebike 等等<br />\n仿淘寶online platform, hktv<br />\n新電視台, viutv<br />\n仲有好多好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有邊一樣係真真正正獲得我地支持而又普及化到？<br />\n政府垃圾係關事，但我地自己香港市民都唔支持其實先係主要原因<br />\n所有野都三分鐘，爭取民主係咁，hktv mall 又係咁。乜都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地一個淘寶就買曬全港豬既心<br />\n仲其實逐步滲透入香港<br />\n講到根本原因，就係冇本冇優惠俾到我地，冇著數就唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n典型資本思考模式，窮人含撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n冇野係無中生有<br />\n宜家普及緊嘅野都一定曾經未普及過<br />\n但當有人帶個新idea 出黎，唔好只係諗佢會點死點唔好點賺錢有幾多漏洞同帶頭抵制，相信帶個idea 出黎既人已經要還神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8184dddc67fd92145b648982acbbc410b4c7a908","tid":415650,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T12:27:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">收皮啦波台狗</span>"},{"pid":"03338fe813da1ca03e331fdd95a5f5a85cd95e13","tid":415650,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T12:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">收皮啦波台狗</span></blockquote><br />\n我動漫台嘅post仲多過波台都話我波台狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3d9f8076130543615b188f1c6ead97bf5a0227","tid":415650,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T12:43:16.000Z","msg":"發覺唔少話香港電子交易好落後嘅人都幾弱智下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/415738/page/1?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/415738/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n<br />\n香港電子交易根本夠用<br />\n近排呀誠哥同馬雲合作推支那寶 唔怪得要吹奏下電子收費啦"},{"pid":"4c0d24cf7eb841e9a350c6bb4ab548110249fa23","tid":415650,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T12:45:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發覺唔少話香港電子交易好落後嘅人都幾弱智下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/415738/page/1?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/415738/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港電子交易根本夠用<br />\n近排呀誠哥同馬雲合作推支那寶 唔怪得要吹奏下電子收費啦</span></blockquote><br />\n好似支港01咁 平時扮晒親民 撐泛民個啲咁 <br />\n大是大非個陣就將輿論帶向撐支共個邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}